title: Gay Pride Flag Watch Face
summary: Provides Gay Pride Watch Face for round and square Wear Smartwatches
description: Provides Gay Pride Watch Face for your Smartwatch. In the future release there will be a configuration page that will contain options like date display and color of the watch's hands.It may take few minutes for the new watch face to appear. You may want to try tapping "Resync Apps" in the Android Wear App on your phone. If, after doing this, you still don't see the new watch face in your Android Wear app, you can also try rebooting your phone and watch.
descriptionHTML:
Provides Gay Pride Watch Face for your Smartwatch. In the future release there will be a configuration page that will contain options like date display and color of the watch's hands.

It may take few minutes for the new watch face to appear. You may want to try tapping "Resync Apps" in the Android Wear App on your phone. If, after doing this, you still don't see the new watch face in your Android Wear app, you can also try rebooting your phone and watch.
